'''''Luofu Myths: Haunted House''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[The Xianzhou Luofu]] in the chapter [[Luofu Myths]].

==Steps==
# Speak to Sushang and Guinaifen
# Investigate the odd billboard
# Investigate the abnormally posted wanted poster
# Investigate the haunted residence's secrets and continue onward
# Go through the locked gate and continue
# Open the safe and take out the deed
# Speak with the heliobus
# Speak to Sushang and Guinaifen

